  theme_ai_color uses environment variables THEME_AI_CMD or THEME_AI_HTTP_URL to generate colors based on
  item prompts, with a fallback to random colors. Usage involves setting these environment variables plus
  optional THEME_AI_MAX_ITEMS and THEME_AI_TIMEOUT. Tests were performed running the theme_ai_color check
  and verifying theme roll with AI commands as expected. Next steps include configuring a local AI agent
  endpoint to enable dynamic theming.

